des:
LI News Radio (103.9) is Long Island’s only FM news station. Enable our skill then say "Alexa open one oh three nine l. i. news radio".

Broadcasting LIVE from Islip’s MacArthur Airport, we are bringing news, traffic and weather to our listeners. LI News Radio Studios are located at: Islip MacArthur Airport 100 Arrival Ave, Ronkonkoma, NY 11779 LI News Radio Offices are located at: 3075 Veterans Memorial Highway Ronkonkoma, NY 11779 More information can be found at http://linewsradio.com/
